OL,6,FThe Taliban has ordered domestic and
OL,7,Fforeign charities working in
OL,8,FAfghanistan to stop employing women, it
OL,9,Fhas been reported.
OL,11,FA letter from the regime's Economy
OL,12,FMinister Qari Din Mohammed Hanif warned
OL,13,Fthat any non-governmental organisation
OL,14,F(NGOs) not complying with the order
OL,15,Fwill have their operating license
OL,16,Frevoked.
OL,18,FThe contents of the letter were
OL,19,Fconfirmed to The Associated Press (AP)
OL,20,Fon Saturday by ministry spokesman,
OL,21,FAbdul Rahman Habib.
OL,3,CAnger after Taliban orders NGOs in
OL,4,CAfghanistan to stop employing women
